title: Garmin MapSource Topo Portugal TopoLusitania v0.81
description:
Portugal TopoLusitania v0.81 (with Madeira and Azores)

Released version: v0.81 

Manufacturer's homepage: <a href="
http://sites.google.com/site/topolusitania/Home" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://sites.google.com/site/topolusitania/Home</a>

Transparent, non routable map 
10 m contour lines in Portugal mainland
20 contour lines Madeira and Azores.

Includes roads, unpaved roads, rivers, dams etc.

In Madeira includes the "Levadas" coded as pipelines (official data) or
rivers ( Net colected tracks)

Includes the Desertas and Selvagens small islands
